==How does the level land work?==
If you want to make a big pile of land into the same height you should use the level land button.

:#Start by clicking and holding down the mouse where you want to start.
:#*The height of the leveled land will be the same height as the land where you started.<br><br>
:#Then drag the mouse to the end of the area you want to level.<br>[[File:en/Manual/Level land before.png|center|frame|View when an area is selected]]<br><br>
:#When satisfied with the area release the button and the area should then be leveled.<br>[[File:en/Manual/Level land after.png|center|frame|View after the area has been leveled]]